---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Operational Intelligence for Building Materials Distributors"
  description="Real-time dashboards, modern data pipelines, and proactive inventory alerts for building materials distributors. Built on top of SAP, NetSuite, and existing ERPs."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6">
        Operational Intelligence for<br />Building Materials Distributors
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        We build the data infrastructure and dashboards that replace your Excel
        dependency — on top of the ERP you already run.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION 1: Real-Time Operational Dashboards -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-blue-500">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"></line>
            <line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"></line>
            <polyline points="7 10 10 7 13 10 17 7"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Real-Time Operational Dashboards</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Your team shouldn't wait until Friday to know what happened Monday. We
        build dashboards your purchasing, operations, and finance teams open
        every morning.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Purchasing dashboards:</span> Inventory levels, reorder points, exception management across all warehouses</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Operations dashboards:</span> Warehouse performance, fulfillment metrics, transfer tracking</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Finance dashboards:</span> COGS, landed cost analysis, PO tracking, budget vs. actual</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">15-minute data refresh</span> — not weekly Excel exports</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Browser-based</span> — no software to install, accessible from any device</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Built in Streamlit</span> — modern, fast, customizable</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION 2: Modern Data Pipelines -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-blue-500">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="5" cy="6" r="3"></circle>
            <path d="M8 6h8"></path>
            <circle cx="19" cy="6" r="3"></circle>
            <circle cx="5" cy="18" r="3"></circle>
            <path d="M8 18h8"></path>
            <circle cx="19" cy="18" r="3"></circle>
            <path d="M5 9v6"></path>
            <path d="M19 9v6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Modern Data Pipelines</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Your ERP has the data. We build the infrastructure that gets it out —
        automatically, accurately, and continuously.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300">Automated extraction from SAP ByDesign, NetSuite, or similar ERPs via <span class="text-white font-medium">Fivetran</span></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300">Cloud data warehouse in <span class="text-white font-medium">Snowflake</span> with Bronze/Silver/Gold architecture</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-8">
          <span class="text-blue-500 font-mono text-sm mt-0.5 shrink-0">B</span>
          <span class="text-slate-400"><span class="text-slate-300 font-medium">Bronze:</span> Raw data exactly as it comes from your ERP</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-8">
          <span class="text-blue-500 font-mono text-sm mt-0.5 shrink-0">S</span>
          <span class="text-slate-400"><span class="text-slate-300 font-medium">Silver:</span> Cleaned, validated, and standardized</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-8">
          <span class="text-blue-500 font-mono text-sm mt-0.5 shrink-0">G</span>
          <span class="text-slate-400"><span class="text-slate-300 font-medium">Gold:</span> Business-ready metrics and KPIs your team actually needs</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">0.00% data variance</span> — our validation standard</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">No manual exports, ever</span></span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SOLUTION 3: Proactive Inventory Alerts -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-blue-500">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M18 8A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 7-3 9-3 9h18s-3-2-3-9"></path>
            <path d="M13.73 21a2 2 0 0 1-3.46 0"></path>
            <line x1="12" y1="2" x2="12" y2="4"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold">Proactive Inventory Alerts</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl">
        Stop finding out about problems after customers call.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300">Stockout prediction factoring in <span class="text-white font-medium">overseas lead times (90-120 days)</span> and <span class="text-white font-medium">domestic suppliers (3-5 days)</span></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300">Safety stock monitoring with automatic exception flagging</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Multi-warehouse visibility</span> — see inventory across all locations in a single view</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-medium">Transfer tracking</span> — know what's moving between warehouses and when</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-300">Automated alerts <span class="text-white font-medium">before</span> thresholds are breached</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE DON'T DO -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-10">What we don't do</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-5">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-400">We don't replace your ERP. We make it more useful.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-400">We don't do SAP customization projects. We build an intelligence layer on top.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-400">We don't build chatbots or AI toys. We build production systems your team runs on daily.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-400">We don't sell software licenses. You own everything we build.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-500 mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
          <span class="text-slate-400">We don't subcontract. Vinh architects and builds your system directly.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ENGAGEMENT MODEL -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">How engagements work</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Discovery Call</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-500 font-medium mb-1">30-60 min</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Free</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mt-auto">We learn about your operation. No pitch deck.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Paid AI Audit</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-500 font-medium mb-1">2-4 weeks</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">$10,000 - $15,000</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mt-auto">Map every data flow, identify bottlenecks, deliver ROI report.</p>
        </div>
        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Phased Implementation</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-blue-500 font-medium mb-1">8-16 weeks</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">$20,000 - $50,000+</p>
          <p class="text-slate-400 mt-auto">Build pipeline, dashboards, and alerts. Each phase delivers working tools.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-slate-400 text-sm">
        Every engagement starts with the audit. If we can't find enough ROI, we'll tell you.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ERP COMPATIBILITY -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-10 text-center">Works with your existing ERP</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">SAP ByDesign</p>
          <span class="inline-block mt-3 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full">Proven</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">SAP S/4HANA</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">NetSuite</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Sage</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Microsoft Dynamics</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-800/50 border border-slate-700 rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Legacy / custom ERPs</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-2">assessed during audit</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-slate-400 text-sm max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We've validated our approach with SAP ByDesign. The architecture works with any ERP with an API or data export.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BOTTOM CTA -->
  <section class="bg-slate-950 py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to see what your data can do?</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-8">
        <a
          href="https://links.zenprocess.ai/widget/booking/rcoKJifJJA46bRI9fTEr"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        >
          Book a Discovery Call
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-slate-400">
        Or email <a href="mailto:info@zenprocess.ai" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400 underline">info@zenprocess.ai</a> | <a href="tel:+18329742818" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-400 underline">(832) 974-2818</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
